ArtyTorrent Pack 72-House Drum Loops 130-139bpm-WAV
---------------------------------------------------

A variety of 4/4 house loops. A mixture of funky, progressive and old skool house samples.
Tempo ranges from 130-139 bpm.

Torrent contains 6 RAR files with 124 loops
-------------------------------------------
Brazil Elec 130-138 (6 loops)
Chicago Fire House 130-139 (18 loops)
Elab House 130 (6 loops)
Magix MM 130 (28 loops)
Misc House 130-139 (51 loops)
SF Full Loops 130-138 (15 loops)

Samples are from a variety of sources including CDs by EastWest, Ueberschall, Sony/Sonic Foundry, Elab, and Magix, and have all been normalized and acidized as 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz. Approx tempo is included in each filename.

Some loops with more of a techno/trance feel will be posted later.
